<div class="petition-text">
  <p class="lead">
    <i class="fa fa-quote-left" aria-hidden="true"></i> The Israeli-Palestinian conflict is responsible for horrendous misery and suffering on both sides.
  </p>
  <p class="lead">
    We call on our governments to renew their efforts to foster the conditions necessary for a resolution to the conflict.
  </p>
  <p class="lead">
    We call on the Palestinian leadership to recognise Israel's right to a peaceful existence and to commit to non-violence.
  </p>
  <p class="lead">
    And we call on the Israeli government to commit to the creation of a Palestinian state and to end settlement building in the occupied territories. <i class="fa fa-quote-right" aria-hidden="true"></i>
  </p>
</div>

<div class="text-center counter">
  <span class="counter-number">2,567</span>
  <small class="text-muted counter-text">signatures</small>
</div>

<div class="container sign-petition text-right">
  <%= link_to(fa_icon('pencil', text: 'Sign petition').html_safe, new_signature_path, class: 'btn alert-warning') %>
</div>

<%= render 'share_petition' %>
